<DOC><DOCNO> ZF32-168-059 </DOCNO><DOCID>10 854 928</DOCID><JOURNAL>SuperGroup Magazine  May-June 1991 v11 n3 p32(1)* Full Text COPYRIGHT SuperGroup Magazine 1991.andM;</JOURNAL><TITLE>HotKey/3000 version A.1.4 available. (from Riviera Software)andM;</TITLE><DESCRIPT>Company:   Riviera Software Inc. (Product development).andO;Product:   HotKey/3000 A.1.4 (Utility program) (Product development)HP 3000 (Minicomputer) (Computer programs).andO;Topic:     Product DevelopmentUtility Programs.andM;</DESCRIPT><TEXT>Riviera Software has begun shipping version A. 1.4 of its HotKey/3000application switcher.andP;  HotKey allows users to switch between programs runningas if they were logged in different sessions.andP;  To select the program toactivate, users use a special hotkey they can define.andP;  Version A.1.4 allowsusers to switch from one program to another by using a single keystroke inboth block mode and character mode without using function keys.andP;  A newfeature also allows users to switch directly between programs without goingthrough the HotKey menu.andP;  HotKey now supports up to eight UDC files andoffers your programs the option to accept data from a file rather than from$STDIN so that some initial commands can be executed directly.andM;For more information contact Riviera Software, 7901 Havenwood Drive, Austin,TX 78759; (512) 346-0962; fax (512) 338-1455.andO;</TEXT></DOC>